Having an option like that at lower levels, when spec levels are lower, Flappy doesn't give mana regen (or even pre-flappy), and pre-KEI, would make a big difference in how pre-50 wizards could contribute and would be perceived in groups. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=torcerarcana>Torcer Arcana</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Arcanist</span><br>  Posts: 3645<br> <font color=#ffffff>(4/29/03 1:44:14 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=26268.topic&index=55>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Re:Problem</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Why does it always come down to people saying &quot;we are already balanced&quot; and then throwing in &quot;at level 65 with tons of AA points and the best gear in the game (FT15, etc.)&quot;? We shouldn't need all of that to be balanced with average people who don't have all of that.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
