<br>
And KEI wont be available on a newbie server (ditto for the outrageous melee weapons), so that naturally balances too. I played pre-kunark and casters were balanced fine (overbalanced really) against melee with level appropriate weapons.<br>
<br>
Again, as with recent threads by Ray, I dont have any real problem with his idea. SoE *are* gonna have to come up with interesting new ideas for the next expansion .. and the one after that. Unless we are gonna rehash old ideas all the time we have to come up with new lines of spells for every class and this general line for ours seems fine to me, even if the posters here dont yet agree on ratios and stuff.<br>
